The set of GBATEK-documented BIOS-RAM-Usage addresses and well-known constants
(NDS7 BIOS CRC, boot task/message values at 0x027FF880/884, cart chip-ID
layout, 0x027FFE00 cart header copy, etc.) populated in src/cart/loader.ts
were cross-referenced from guac's emu/nds/mem/init.go. The address values are
derived from GBATEK (https://problemkaputt.de/gbatek.htm), the canonical
Nintendo DS documentation.

